<item>
            <title>[LUDOC-34] Section 15.2.2 - use &apos;lustre_rmmod&apos; instead of shell comands</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-34</link>
                <project id="10070" key="LUDOC">Lustre Documentation</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;In section 15.2.2 module removal does not use lustre_rmmod&lt;br/&gt;
This:&lt;br/&gt;
Note&lt;br/&gt;
To remove all Lustre modules, run:&lt;br/&gt;
$ lctl modules | awk &apos;&lt;/p&gt;
{print $2}
&lt;p&gt;&apos; | xargs rmmod&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Should be:&lt;br/&gt;
Note&lt;br/&gt;
To remove all Lustre modules, run:&lt;br/&gt;
$ lustre_rmmod&lt;/p&gt;</description>
